Package: RDistanceMatrix
Type: Package
Title: Useful Functions For Building Isochrones And Related Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Chris
Maintainer: Chris <c.jamesbailey@gmail.com>
Description: Builds isochrones using either the google distance matrix API or the Mapbox API. 
    Contains functions to fetch the population and employment within the isochrone.
